	<Title>
		Fruit how to: Grilled fruit slices
	</Title>
	<Body>
		&lt;p&gt;Want a new way to enjoy fresh fruit? Grill it! Cut apples, pears or peaches into chunks, brush lightly with canola oil and sprinkle with cinnamon. Place on skewers or wrap in foil. Grill on low heat for 3 to 5 minutes.&lt;/p&gt;
